Do they have a solid plate in bed instead of a rust?
Get it out!
Or at most for a bed for unloved guests and for a single night.
They should also use the plate with ventilation holes (if none are already in it) and mattresses with spring skeleton and 15 cm minimum height with so-called pocket spring core and fine cushions.
Polyurethane mattresses do not belong on such a base.
Latex or sandwich mattresses (possibly also combinations of latex and coconut) are suitable for non-adjustable slatted rusts with 14 to 18 spring strips (lamellas), always paying off rusts with a larger slatted number, i.e. from 28 or more spring strips, with lumbar support in the lumbar vertebrae area and the possibility to regulate the slatted hardness.
On adjustable lamellar rust, no mattresses with feather skeleton belong, because they do not react to the ergonomic adjustment.
In addition to adjusting the stiffness of the spring strips, special flexible shoulder modules are also offered.
This is about a special attachment of the spring strips, which makes it possible to press in the spring strips or even to angle them in such a way that they allow the shoulder of the sleeper to sink in at once.
Especially for men with broad shoulders an important thing.
There are even mattress manufacturers who have started to use soft zones for the shoulder area in men's mattresses.
The ladies are also thought of - they are given these soft zones in the hip area.
For the most demanding customers, point-heavy wing suspension systems (Lattoflex) or grates with point-heavy contact pads with so-called multitorsion suspension are determined.
The pressure is distributed over several points, which reduces the voltage.
But - if you use a bad (too large and full) pillow for the right mattress and proper rust, most of the benefits are lost again.
