Extracts of red peppers stimulate blood circulation, so the weaker sex gets comfortably warm when sleeping.
And today's favorites?
Cold foam mattresses (he has larger pores with destroyed cell structure and is therefore more breathable than standard polyurethane and also much more flexible).
